{"tid":1944654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美司法部︰蓄意傳播新冠病毒或構成恐怖主義罪","createTime":"2020-03-26T13:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T15:21:46.000Z","uid":193217,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"917a397ab4070fe837f26dc71a147041552b9e77","tid":1944654,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"美國新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診個案持續急增，美國有線新聞網（CNN）引述副司法部長羅森（Jeffrey Rosen）周二（24日）在給司法部高層官員、檢察官及執法機構的備忘錄中指出，新型冠狀病毒似乎符合「生物物質」的法定定義，因此蓄意傳播的行為可適用於美國對恐怖定義的相關法規。<br />\n<br />\n羅森表示，不會容忍任何威脅或企圖把新冠病毒用於對付美國人的行為，必須竭盡所能在疫情下保護美國人的權利和安全。<br />\n<br />\n截至香港時間今日（26日）下午3時，美國累計69,194宗確診病例、1050人死亡，確診個案逾半來自紐約州。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328a9a8111358e195681739f2cd5bf062e0debf8","tid":1944654,"uid":193217,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"睇你支共仲敢唔敢講<br />\n一set到恐怖主義就全球都要郁你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a8a4a90acd6f89250c0c3794ba757406bc5848","tid":1944654,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:02:13.000Z","msg":"蓄意輸出患病人口係咪恐怖主義國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d36a07b95e127fc1cd366a1ee841b3d8a98b76","tid":1944654,"uid":234589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:02:27.000Z","msg":"CCP (70yrs)"},{"pid":"481eb31160df6258cacf3741f0a094c50a2f4e54","tid":1944654,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"328a9a8111358e195681739f2cd5bf062e0debf8","tid":1944654,"uid":193217,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"睇你支共仲敢唔敢講<br />\n一set到恐怖主義就全球都要郁你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit